<li><a href="/wiki/File:Wikisource-logo.svg" class="image" title="Wikisource-logo.svg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4c/Wikisource-logo.svg/15px-Wikisource-logo.svg.png" width="15" height="16" border="0" /></a> "<a href="http://en.wikisource.org/wiki/Catholic_Encyclopedia_(1913)/Mysticism" class="extiw" title="s:Catholic Encyclopedia (1913)/Mysticism">Mysticism</a>" in the 1913 <i>Catholic Encyclopedia</i>.</li>
</ul>
