<li>Underhill's <a href="http://www.ccel.org/ccel/underhill/mysticism.v.html" class="external text" title="http://www.ccel.org/ccel/underhill/mysticism.v.html" rel="nofollow">"Historical Sketch"</a> of Christian Mysticism from <i>Mysticism</i> (1911)</li>
